              <p class="para">Voir aussi les livres rouges d'IBM <a href="http://www.redbooks.ibm.com/abstracts/gg243376.html" class="ulink" title="http://www.redbooks.ibm.com/abstracts/gg243376.html">TCP/IP Tutorial and Technical Overview</a>.</p>
